{"id":281855,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-两会召开各地警车云集北京，上访维权者/","date":"2013-03-03T09:15:50Z","modified":"2013-03-03T09:15:50Z","title":"维权网 | 两会召开各地警车云集北京，上访维权者成为“猎物”（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员田静民报道）全国两会召开前夕，北京的大街小巷到处都能看见各地不同牌照的警车。而地方警车的主要职能，便是在北京警察的配合下大肆抓捕上访维权人士。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日上午</span><span>，本网信息员在北京南站开阳桥以西地段方圆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>米</span><span>走了一圈儿，竟看到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>多辆各地公、检、法的警车云集在此。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>因权利受到侵害而成为访民的各地维权者，已成为地方官府、公安的猎物。他们在地方上逃避种种监控，甚至是沿路的追堵，终于到达北京，渴望能借两会之机，面见代表或向有关部门陈述冤情，以期多年的诉求尽快得到解决。然而，等待他们的是在没有任何法律程序，也不出示任何手续、没有理由的情况下随时都会遭到绑架和关押，不仅剥夺了他们的信访权，更严重侵犯了他们的人身自由权。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在北京南站的开阳桥附近方圆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>米</span><span>的范围内，有河北省警车</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>辆，吉林省</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>辆，河南省</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>辆，山东省</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>辆，辽宁省、陕西省、内蒙古各一辆。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>部分车牌号如下：冀</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-DA283</span><span>警，冀</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-DB210</span><span>警，冀</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-DA026</span><span>警，冀</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-D2996</span><span>警，冀</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-AA581</span><span>警，冀</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-AA422</span><span>警，冀</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-J B168</span><span>警，冀</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-J 0715</span><span>警，冀</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-B 3737</span><span>警，冀</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-DA274</span><span>警，冀</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-J 0780</span><span>警，冀</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-J 1908</span><span>警，冀</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-CD057</span><span>警，吉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-FA016</span><span>警，吉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-FA 508</span><span>警，吉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-DA090</span><span>警，吉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-CA088</span><span>警，吉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-FD021</span><span>警，吉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-F 0299</span><span>警，豫</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-HA 257</span><span>警，豫</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-AA896</span><span>警，豫</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-CA 015</span><span>警，豫</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-AA339</span><span>警，豫</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-AA 896</span><span>警，豫</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-AB712</span><span>警，鲁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-E 9019</span><span>警，鲁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-AA33</span><span>警，鲁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-K 0299</span><span>警，鲁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-K0328</span><span>警，陕</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-AD 385</span><span>警，蒙</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-F0211</span><span>警，辽</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-BB127</span><span>警。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Ac1jE04NNsQ/UTL3i0vFLDI/AAAAAAAAeUQ/Sjqlq_ts2Is/s1600/P010313_1729.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"208\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Ac1jE04NNsQ/UTL3i0vFLDI/AAAAAAAAeUQ/Sjqlq_ts2Is/s320/P010313_1729.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-6qHgPu08XBM/UTL3kc7-rpI/AAAAAAAAeUY/9ThXi6qYilM/s1600/P020313_1240%5B01%5D.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"199\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-6qHgPu08XBM/UTL3kc7-rpI/AAAAAAAAeUY/9ThXi6qYilM/s320/P020313_1240%5B01%5D.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Uulsgr6LXG0/UTL3nfIMoJI/AAAAAAAAeUg/52sdVsxbAss/s1600/P020313_12391.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"209\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Uulsgr6LXG0/UTL3nfIMoJI/AAAAAAAAeUg/52sdVsxbAss/s320/P020313_12391.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p>